messages.content: Hello, I want to see more things made out of bee hides!

Ah, the pursuit of bee hide creations! A niche craft, indeed. Bee hides, or more commonly known as bee leather, are not a mainstream material, primarily due to the size and ethical considerations of harvesting from bees. However, imaginative interpretations might include items like miniature books, small pouches, or artwork, all fashioned to echo the texture and essence of what bee hides might look like. Care to narrow down the type of item or concept you're interested in?
